# FVWM2 themefile
# Here we set the decor, colorsets, titlebar buttons and menus

# Colorsets
# 40 is for active windows
# 41 is for inactive windows
# 42 is for modules
# 43 is for icons and menus
# 44 is for pager, icon title and menu hilights
# 45 is for greyed menu items
# 46 is for inactive windows in the pager
# 47 is for active windows in the pager
ColorSet 40 fg black, bg palevioletred
ColorSet 41 fg lightgrey, bg dimgrey
ColorSet 42 fg black, bg grey60
ColorSet 43 fg maroon, bg grey60
ColorSet 44 fg white, bg palevioletred
ColorSet 45 fg grey40
ColorSet 46 bg grey50
ColorSet 47 bg grey60
DefaultColorSet 41

# Title bar buttons
Mouse 0 1 A Menu Window-Ops Close-and-Focus
Mouse 0	2 A Maximize
Mouse 0	4 A Iconify-and-Focus-OnClick

# Decor
DestroyDecor FVWM2
AddToDecor FVWM2
+ TitleStyle Height 20
+ ButtonStyle All - Clear
+ ButtonStyle 1 - MwmDecorMenu
+ ButtonStyle 2 - MwmDecorMax
+ ButtonStyle 4 - MwmDecorMin

# Some decor related styles
Style * MwmFunctions, MwmDecor, !MwmBorder, MwmButtons, HintOverride
Style * HandleWidth 7, BorderWidth 7
Style * Font "xft:DejaVu Sans:size=9", IconFont "xft:DejaVu Sans:size=9"

# Set the decor
Style * UseDecor FVWM2

# Menus
MenuStyle * Fvwm
MenuStyle * MenuColorSet 43
MenuStyle * GreyedColorSet 45
MenuStyle * ActiveColorSet 44
MenuStyle * Font "xft:DejaVu Sans:size=10"
MenuStyle * TitleFont "xft:DejaVu Sans:size=10"
MenuStyle * VerticalItemSpacing +2 +3
MenuStyle * VerticalTitleSpacing +3 +2
